- Service pages: canonical to self (unique content per service)
- Blog posts: canonical to self
- Paginated content: canonical to page 1 OR rel="prev/next"

**Parameter Handling:**
- UTM parameters: exclude from canonical
- Filter parameters: exclude from index
- Add to next.config.mjs: `trailingSlash: false`

